# Local mount configuration for devcontainer
# Copy this file to mounts.local and customize for your system
#
# Format: target=source
#   target: folder name in /workspaces/today/
#   source: absolute path on your host machine
#
# The generate-compose-override.sh script reads this file and creates
# docker-compose.override.yml with the appropriate volume mounts.
# This runs automatically when you rebuild the container.
#
# Examples:

# Obsidian vault synced via iCloud (macOS)
# vault=/Users/username/Library/Mobile Documents/iCloud~md~obsidian/Documents/vault

# Additional project repositories
# OlderGay.Men=/Users/username/src/rails/OlderGay.Men
